data.content:
Here are the estimated nominal GDP figures for India (in US$ trillions) for the most recent five fiscal years:
- FY 2019‑2020: ~2.87 trillion
- FY 2020‑2021: ~3.05 trillion
- FY 2021‑2022: ~3.17 trillion
- FY 2022‑2023: ~3.53 trillion
- FY 2023‑2024 (estimate): ~3.73 trillion
These numbers are based on data available up to 2024 and are rounded estimates.
